Stage 6 of 8: Find Your People

Darkwind is social. Channels connect the whole game; parties share the
fight and the spoils; clans are player-run organizations with wars and
coffers; kingdoms crown player rulers with their own nobility.

Pick a divine patron when the gods start to notice you. Alignment and
devotion open their own doors.

